{"lemma":"لازِبَةٍ","slug":"لازِبَةٍ","root":"ل.ز.ب","root_slug":"ل-ز-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ل-ز-ب","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"لازِب","root":"لزب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37714"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B2%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37714","headword_ar":"لَازِبٌ","root":"lzb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Adhering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adhesive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cohesive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"clay or mud. (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Being,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remaining, fixed, settled, firm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAra Al$~aYo'u","text_ar":"صَارَ الشَّىْءُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Darobapa laAzibK","text_ar":"ضَرْبَةَ لَازِبٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thing became fixed, settled, firm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and severe:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a constant infliction:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indispensable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"necessary:"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the blow of a sword that sticks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remains fixed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the wound"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Aboo-Bekr, cited in the TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lAzb","text_ar":"لازب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lAzm","text_ar":"لازم"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) the latter is the original word; the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":"being changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and is also used in this phrase: (TA:) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lAzb","text_ar":"لازب"},{"kind":"text","text":", in this in-"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2659},{"kind":"text","text":"stance, is the more chaste. (S.) En-Nábighah says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"falaA taHosibuwna Alxayora laA $ar~a baEodahu\n                      \n                     \n                        walaA taHosibuwna Al$~ar~a Darobapa laAzibi"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Then think ye not that good shall have no evil after it, nor think ye that evil shall be a constant infliction"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) Sgh says, of the conversion of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riwaAgapN","text_ar":"رِوَاغَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyaAgapN","text_ar":"رِيَاغَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of kesreh before it,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA Alqalobu layosa biDarobK laAzibK","text_ar":"هٰذَا القَلْبُ لَيْسَ بِضَرْبٍ لَازِبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This conversion is not a necessary sort."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwg","text_ar":"روغ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}